OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be cloudy with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain, much of the rain
OL,7,Flight and patchy although the odd
OL,8,Fheavier burst possible in the
OL,9,Fafternoon. Some brighter spells with a
OL,10,Fscattering of showers developing later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FBright spells and occasional
OL,13,Fshowers this evening. The showers most
OL,14,Ffrequent in the west and around the
OL,15,Fnorth coast overnight, some drier and
OL,16,Fclearer spells for Belfast and the
OL,17,Feast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
