OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FBright spells and showers, the
OL,6,Fbest of the brightness across Counties
OL,7,FAntrim and Down during the morning.
OL,8,FThe showers could be heavy, perhaps
OL,9,Fthe odd rumble of thunder.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FA dry
OL,12,Fand bright start on Monday, rain then
OL,13,Fpushing in from the southwest. Rain or
OL,14,Fshowers on Tuesday and Wednesday,
OL,15,Fheavy at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
